{"id":756814,"title":"Powerhouse mandel matcha superfood smoothie","titleEn":"Powerhouse Almond Matcha Superfood Smoothie","image":"https://img.spoonacular.com/recipes/756814-556x370.jpg","readyInMinutes":10,"servings":2,"ingredients":["2 spsk usaltet naturligt mandelpålæg","1½ dl usødet mandelmælk","1 medium frossen banan","2 tsk chiafro","1 dl babyspinat, pakket","½ dl frosne mangoklumper","1 spsk matcha grøn te pulver","¾ dl frossen ananas","½ tsk vaniljeekstrakt"],"steps":["Kombiner alle ingredienser i en blender. Bland på høj hastighed, indtil det er glat.","Servér øjeblikkeligt."]}